nodes.text: Miss Coruscant talent and beauty pageant

The Miss Coruscant talent and beauty pageant was a competition held at the planet of Coruscant focused on judging and ranking the talents and the physical attributes of the contestants, who were all female. The competition's winner was rewarded with a bouquet of flowers and a crown that said Miss Coruscant, hence the title of the event.
Shortly before the start of the Clone Wars, the Pa'lowick Larisselle Chatrunis won the Miss Coruscant talent and beauty pageant by beating out the 35 other contestants.
